&lt;div&gt;We’re building a next-gen SaaS channel organization to power a rapidly scaling, product-led growth start-up. We’re looking for a Channel Partner Manager to grow and enable our Enterprise partner ecosystem across VARs, SIs, consulting firms, and traditional channels. You’ll help partners drive customer value and accelerate product-market fit, supporting them from lead generation to enablement and full customer lifecycle management. This is your chance to shape our channel strategy and create meaningful impact at scale.&lt;/div&gt;
