&lt;p&gt;At DevRev, we&#39;re building the future of work with &lt;em&gt;Computer&lt;/em&gt; – your AI teammate. Unlike traditional tools, &lt;em&gt;Computer&lt;/em&gt; unifies all your data sources, tools, and workflows into a single AI-ready platform, giving employees real-time insights, proactive suggestions, and powerful agentic actions. It extends your existing software with AI-native apps and agents that work alongside your teams and customers – updating workflows, coordinating across teams, and eliminating repetitive work. We call this Team Intelligence: human-AI collaboration that breaks down silos, brings people back together, and frees you to solve bigger problems. Backed by Khosla Ventures and Mayfield with $150M+ raised, DevRev is trusted by global companies across industries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of the Revenue organization at DevRev, we are growing our team and hiring talented, ambitious, and AI-native Sales Development Representatives (SDRs) in Austin, Texas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an SDR at DevRev, you will operate at the intersection of sales, AI, and customer intelligence. Your mission will be to expand DevRev&#39;s customer base, generate qualified pipeline, and help shape our go-to-market strategy. Rather than relying solely on traditional prospecting methods, you will leverage AI-powered tools and workflows to identify opportunities, personalize engagement, and build meaningful relationships with prospective customers at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll work closely with Sales, Marketing, Product, and Engineering teams to refine messaging, uncover market insights, and continuously improve how we engage with customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our office is located off 6th Street, and we work in-office three days per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expand our pipeline by identifying and engaging high-quality prospects across target accounts and market segments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Research accounts, stakeholders, and buying signals using AI-powered tools and modern prospecting techniques.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build personalized outreach campaigns across email, phone, text, social, and emerging channels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set up introductory meetings with target influencers and key decision-makers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Qualify prospects by understanding their business challenges, priorities, and goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with Account Executives to develop account strategies and create high-quality pipeline opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leverage AI-assisted workflows to increase productivity while maintaining thoughtful, high-quality engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop, test, and optimize messaging, prompts, and prospecting playbooks to improve conversion rates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Analyze prospect interactions, engagement data, and market trends to continuously improve targeting and outreach effectiveness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain accurate pipeline data and account information within DevRev&#39;s CRM.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Act as the voice of the market by sharing customer insights, objections, and feedback with Product, Engineering, Marketing, and Revenue teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stay current on emerging AI technologies, sales methodologies, and industry trends to continuously evolve your prospecting approach.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
